# CI/CD

## Workflows

| Workflow | When | Purpose |
|----------|------|---------|
| [`.github/workflows/kmp-ci.yml`](.github/workflows/kmp-ci.yml) | Push, PR, manual | Android unit+APK, merge-gate instrumented/iOS, Supabase migration validation |
| [`.github/workflows/supabase-deploy.yml`](.github/workflows/supabase-deploy.yml) | `main` migration push, manual | `supabase db push` to linked project (secrets required) |

### KMP CI jobs (tiered)

- **Push `feature/**`:** `Android CI` â†’ `Release` (Firebase + version bump). Target **&lt;4 min** wall clock.
- **PR / `main` push:** `Android CI`, `Supabase Migrations`, `Android Instrumented UI Tests`, and `iOS Compatibility Signal` run **in parallel**; then `Release`. Target **&lt;7 min** wall clock (emulator + iOS bound).
- **Manual dispatch:** `all`, `android-ci`, `android-instrumented-tests`, `supabase-migrations`, `ios-compatibility`, `release` (reuse APK via optional `source_run_id`).

### Supabase

- **CI validation (no remote writes):** `supabase db start` applies all migrations on ephemeral Postgres; remote smoke via `scripts/verify-supabase-household.sh` on PR/`main` only.
- **Deploy:** `supabase-deploy.yml` runs `db push` on `main` when `supabase/migrations/**` changes. Requires secrets `SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN`, `SUPABASE_DB_PASSWORD`, `SUPABASE_PROJECT_REF`.
- **Android builds:** `SUPABASE_URL` + `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` â†’ `local.properties` via composite setup action.
- **`GOOGLE_SERVICES_JSON`:** enables Crashlytics in CI debug APKs.

### Release job

- Downloads `composeApp-debug-apk`, distributes to Firebase App Distribution, bumps version on **push** (`chore(version): â€¦ [skip ci]`).
- **`release` only dispatch:** reuses APK from latest successful `Android CI` on the branch (or `source_run_id`).

## Change guidelines

- Keep the tiered model: fast feedback on `feature/**` push; merge gate on PR/`main`.
- Do not run `db push` inside KMP CI â€” deploy workflow only.
- Never commit secrets; use GitHub Secrets.
- **CI speed:** merged unit+APK; parallel merge-gate jobs; AVD snapshot cache; shallow checkout; Gradle `setup-gradle` cache; pinned `firebase-tools` with npm cache; Supabase validation parallel on PR/`main` only.

## Firebase App Distribution

- Release notes: branch/SHA + QA checklist excerpt from `firebase-appdistribution-testcases.yaml`.
- Update YAML when shipping UX changes.

## Commits & PRs

- Commit only when user asks; match repo commit message style.
- PRs: behavior change, test plan (unit + instrumented + manual), UI screenshots when relevant.

## Artifacts

- Debug APK: `composeApp-debug-apk` (consumed by `Release` job).
